- Task 1: Increase screenTitle marginBottom 4→20 in Log tab for breathing room
- Task 2a: Add textAlign:center to SetRow prev style to match column header
- Task 2b: Fix checkmark column header width 36→28 to match actual checkCircle width
- Task 3: Add Body Part / Equipment labels to exercise filter bars
- Task 4: Checkbox auto-fills previous weight/reps when fields are empty before starting rest timer
- Task 5: Delete empty sets (null weight and reps) before finishing workout
- Task 6: Remove redundant RestTimerBar (inline card timer is sufficient)
- Task 7: Add Perform Again + Save as Template buttons to workout detail screen; new utils/start-from-session.ts utility
- Task 8: WorkoutMiniBar floating above tab bar when workout is active; minimize button on active workout header navigates back to tabs
